1004
01:08:23,041 --> 01:08:23,884
Vámonos.

1005
01:08:24,084 --> 01:08:27,179
<i>Es todo. Li "Orilla Rellena" Fong
avanza a la final...</i>

1006
01:08:27,379 --> 01:08:29,473
<i>donde enfrentará a Conor Day...</i>

1007
01:08:29,673 --> 01:08:30,849
