01:15:03,982 --> 01:15:05,284
Senséi.

1112
01:15:18,496 --> 01:15:19,882
Dos ramas.

1113
01:15:20,373 --> 01:15:21,508
Un árbol.

1114
01:15:58,453 --> 01:16:00,714
<i>¡Directamente de Beijing, China...</i>

1115
01:16:00,914 --> 01:16:02,924
